    "The tools were not fun, according to the respondents.",
    "They thought the responses the gadget offered were not funny.",
    "Overall, the respondents' attitudes were insignificant and negative and so, H5 was rejected.",
    "Moreover, the student respondents demonstrated positive intent by saying they will utilize ChatGPT for their studies in the future when it came to measuring the behavioral intention to use the learning-based AI tool (Kabra et al., 2023).",
